  <h2 class="h5">Data Split and Training Policy</h2>
  <ul class="list-unstyled mx-auto" style="max-width:800px; text-align:left">
    <li><strong>Training policy:</strong> Participants may use any external data (synthetic/public/proprietary). Only official test sets are restricted.</li>
    <li><strong>Public validation set:</strong> Representative subset with LR frames and ground-truth text for local validation and public leaderboard.</li>
    <li><strong>Private blind test set:</strong> Unseen videos with similar diversity; organizers run submissions to generate final CER scores.</li>
  </ul>

